@BDMS.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5017

### Create user (Service layer)
POST {{BDMS.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jdoe",
  "email": "jdoe@example.com"
}

### Get all users (Service layer)
GET {{BDMS.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Create donor (CQRS command)
POST {{BDMS.Api_HostAddress}}/api/donors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aung Aung",
  "bloodType": "O+",
  "lastDonationDate": "2025-01-10T00:00:00Z"
}

### Get donor by id (CQRS query)
GET {{BDMS.Api_HostAddress}}/api/donors/{{donorId}}
Accept: application/json
